<h2>範例</h2>

<p>將以下的 "這裡"，替換成 data-ride="carousel" 使其能夠運作</p>

<div class="demo">
  <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel slide" 這裡>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="http://lorempixel.com/g/640/360/" alt="First slide">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="http://lorempixel.com/g/640/360/" alt="Second slide">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="http://lorempixel.com/g/640/360/" alt="Third slide">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>將以下的 "這裡"，替換成相同的 id 名稱 #carouselExampleSlides2 使其能夠運作</p>

<div class="demo">
  <div id="carouselExampleSlides2" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="這裡" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="這裡" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="這裡" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="http://lorempixel.com/g/640/360/" alt="First slide">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="http://lorempixel.com/g/640/360/" alt="Second slide">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="http://lorempixel.com/g/640/360/" alt="Third slide">
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="這裡" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="這裡" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

